* GF180MCU-D scaffold-only class-B differential/push-pull RF PA.
* Pins: gnda vdda rfin rfout vbias
* Status: topology seed only. The current RFPA runner is single-ended; the
* ideal splitter/combiner below is a placeholder for future differential flows.
.subckt {{netlist_name}} gnda vdda rfin rfout vbias

* Ideal single-ended-to-differential drive placeholder.
CINBLK rfin gate_rf {{ Cin_value }}
* Large DC leak prevents the AC-coupled splitter input from floating in OP/AC.
RINLEAK gate_rf vbias 1G
EINP gatep vbias gate_rf gnda 0.5
EINN gaten vbias gate_rf gnda -0.5
RGP gatep vbias {{ Rbias_value }}
RGN gaten vbias {{ Rbias_value }}
RGSTOPP gatep gatep_int {{ Rg_value }}
RGSTOPN gaten gaten_int {{ Rg_value }}

* Push-pull output devices.
MMP drainp gatep_int gnda gnda nfet_03v3.12 l={{ M1_L }}u w={{ M1_W }}u m={{ M1_M }}
MMN drainn gaten_int gnda gnda nfet_03v3.12 l={{ M2_L }}u w={{ M2_W }}u m={{ M2_M }}

* Idealized RF chokes.
LRFCP vdda drainp 200n
LRFCN vdda drainn 200n
RRFCP vdda drainp 10k
RRFCN vdda drainn 10k

* Ideal differential-to-single-ended combiner placeholder.
EOUT rfout gnda drainp drainn 0.5
ROUTLEAK rfout gnda 1G

.ends {{netlist_name}}
